Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.75,0:00:07.08,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,It appeared as though humanity \Nwould be destroyed by the demons.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.13,0:00:15.30,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,But a single mage saved them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.52,0:00:27.60,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,He was called the Wizard King,\Nand he became a legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:32.53,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,Th-There's an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.53,0:00:34.26,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The capital!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.26,0:00:36.39,main,Messenger,0000,0000,0000,,The capital is under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.23,0:00:44.44,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The Clover Kingdom fell under attack\Nwhile the Wizard King was absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.17,0:00:49.03,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The royal capital was in flames, \Nand people fled from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.11,0:00:54.67,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You're stronger than me, right? Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:57.68,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Get out here, Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.68,0:01:00.76,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! There are people \Nout there who need our help!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.45,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.47,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:05.08,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you plan to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.08,0:01:10.52,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even know the full situation yet, \Nand you can't sense magic at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.52,0:01:12.27,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to where it's noisiest!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.27,0:01:14.40,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you think you're \Nan animal or something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:17.75,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:20.03,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.03,0:01:22.62,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Asta, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.07,0:01:27.12,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd rather not take orders \Nfrom me, but listen well, Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.45,0:01:29.77,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go after Leo and that Black Bulls boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:31.71,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,and after I've joined them,\Nwe'll head to the north district.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:34.28,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Silver Eagles, I ask that you \Nhead to the central district,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:36.21,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,where the magic is strongest.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:38.66,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Roses, head to the east district!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:42.01,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather not take orders from a man, \Nbut I suppose I don't have a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.51,0:01:46.89,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Golden Dawn, split into two teams and head \Nto the west and northwest districts!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:48.24,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:52.15,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll just have \Nto save dessert for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.15,0:01:55.62,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,If we fail to protect the royal capital, \Nwe'll bring shame upon the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:57.40,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Do not let the enemy escape, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.40,0:01:58.90,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:12.71,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Little girl... Do you \Nlike the Clover Kingdom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.05,0:02:15.11,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I-I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.72,0:02:20.00,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,So please... stop this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:24.47,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:28.02,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,So the town... the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.18,0:02:30.94,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,And you, too, little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.64,0:02:33.40,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.44,0:02:38.11,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,The members of the Magic Knights moved out,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.11,0:02:40.49,italics,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,and when Asta arrived...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:47.57,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:07.89,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I would always close my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:12.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And cower at reality
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:16.91,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand the idea
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.91,0:03:21.28,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Of just making excuses to give up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:22.38,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:23.54,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be near you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.54,0:03:24.68,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Any minute now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.68,0:03:28.08,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait right there
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:28.08,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(The decisive battle is still a long way off)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.08,0:03:30.16,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Black and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:36.08,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give up on giving up
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.08,0:03:39.59,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And get the world on my side
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.59,0:03:43.23,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm looking for the reason I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.23,0:03:48.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time somewhere under this sky
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.47,0:03:54.32,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Break through the tearful nights
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.32,0:03:57.61,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And head where the light shines
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.61,0:04:01.44,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to keep my promise
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.44,0:04:04.99,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deliver it to you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.99,0:04:08.96,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,shape of love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.54,0:04:16.73,Ep Title,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Wild Magic Dance
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.92,main,Man,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:44.69,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,North District
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.12,0:04:52.99,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Someone finally shows up, \Nand it's a Black Bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.99,0:04:55.41,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,And a little kid to boot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.72,0:04:58.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from her, you crazy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.58,0:05:05.53,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You fool! You won't be able to stop \Nmy army with that rusty sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.68,0:05:09.60,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.76,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,I was so scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.76,0:05:14.93,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You really acted fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.39,0:05:17.01,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous, so stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.01,0:05:17.98,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.98,0:05:22.82,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I see. You're the one \Nwith the anti-magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.42,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:27.87,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Man, gimme a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.87,0:05:30.81,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,No one asked the bottom-ranked Black Bulls
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:34.16,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,or a piece of trash like you with no magic
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.16,0:05:36.41,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,to show up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:44.92,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.92,0:05:51.51,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Central District
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.51,0:05:54.55,main,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think you're going to get away with...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.12,0:05:57.96,main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,What? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.39,main,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give it to you, just—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.60,0:06:07.53,main,People,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Silver Eagles!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.53,0:06:10.53,sign_8905_87_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Captain of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Nozel Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:13.91,sign_8905_87_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Member of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Solid Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:13.91,top,Man 3,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights have come to save us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:16.70,top,Man 2,0000,0000,0000,,The captain is here! We're saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.39,sign_8905_87_Captain_of_the_S,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,912)}Member of the Silver Eagles\N{\fs30}Nebra Silva
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:19.46,top,Lady,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Nozel! Lord Solid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.46,0:06:21.04,main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Nebra!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.04,0:06:23.79,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Citizens, fall behind us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:28.80,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,West District
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:35.86,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,What are these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.86,0:06:37.83,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Every time we knock them down,\Nthey get up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.15,0:06:46.07,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,I was planning to have dessert when we \Ngot back, but I think I've lost my appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.07,0:06:51.07,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,East District
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.07,0:06:55.14,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, these things are gross, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:59.45,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed. I feel nauseous just looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:02.45,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Also, be mindful of your tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.96,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:07.85,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:13.47,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Northwest District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.47,0:07:15.69,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.69,0:07:17.09,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:19.06,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Do they have some kind of weakness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.97,0:07:24.44,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,It matters not. There's no point \Nin wasting time trying to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.44,0:07:29.44,sign_6799_65_North_District,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,North District
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.44,0:07:31.21,main,noelle,0000,0000,0000,,They're disgusting...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.21,0:07:32.95,main,leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Is my rival safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.68,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,We can look for the\NBlack Bulls boy later, Leo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:42.58,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,These things possess magic, \Nbut they aren't alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:43.99,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:48.09,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just have to crush them \Nuntil they can't get back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:50.46,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,See if you can take my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:53.48,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Spiral Flames!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:57.35,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Magic: Sol Linea!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.60,0:08:04.77,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,A-Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.78,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Steel Creation Magic: Fierce Spiral Lance!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.70,0:08:20.92,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, you fight in such a vulgar manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.67,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:26.87,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,die in elegance and beauty!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:30.42,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Glass Creation Magic: Verre Fleur!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.12,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Shatter before my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:41.26,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Sand Creation Magic: \NSand-Armored Heavy Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.56,0:08:47.29,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Wind Magic: Towering Tornado!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:52.69,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,If you're hurt, please come see me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.70,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,I will heal you with my \NDream-Healing Flower Cradle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:09:00.07,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Filthy creatures, stay away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.07,0:09:02.95,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Quit grossing my Sis out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.51,0:09:06.59,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Earth Creation Magic: Raging Mother Goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.44,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Captain."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.22,0:09:23.20,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow anyone to touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.01,0:09:28.59,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Briar Creation Magic: \NCorpse-Hunting Briar Trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.11,0:09:32.66,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You're all eyesores!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:36.11,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Slashing Sea Serpent!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.79,0:09:39.13,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Mist Magic: Solid Mist Clones!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:49.48,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. They weren't much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.55,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Accept your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:58.13,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Mercury Magic: Rain of Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.80,0:10:04.47,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Punishment for the crime of \Ndaring to threaten the people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.20,0:10:06.35,main,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.18,0:10:11.31,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Flame Creation Magic: Leo Rugiens!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.19,0:10:18.57,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Burn to ashes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:20.28,main,Man A,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:21.32,main,Woman A,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.32,0:10:22.71,main,Man B,0000,0000,0000,,They're so powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.71,0:10:24.23,main,Man C,0000,0000,0000,,They're too amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.08,0:10:35.48,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:38.51,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,That voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.52,0:10:43.72,italics,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:47.26,italics,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he managed to mow down \Nthat many of them with just a sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:49.46,italics,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,He's so strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.46,0:10:52.60,italics,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,What a stupidly straightforward \Nway of fighting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.87,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,He's just too interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.87,0:11:00.96,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,This is why he's my perfect rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.52,0:11:08.15,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,My magic runs my own mana through corpses,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.15,0:11:11.16,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,making them move in any way \NI want. It's wraith magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:19.59,italics,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,That guy's attacks instantly cut through \Nthe mana in the corpses and erases it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:24.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.76,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you, mister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.09,0:11:28.73,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:35.02,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you attacking \Ninnocent people, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.69,0:11:39.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:55.08,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Number Four, Jimmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.59,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,"Innocent"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.59,0:12:01.92,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who doesn't understand my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.31,0:12:07.75,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,is a sinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.87,0:12:23.44,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you attacking \Ninnocent people, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:27.74,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to defeat you, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.03,0:12:43.51,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Number Four, Jimmy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:47.01,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,"Innocent"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:50.35,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who doesn't understand my magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:56.19,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,is a sinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:11.39,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,They keep coming, one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.39,0:13:14.37,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,But they're no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.37,0:13:18.29,main,Alecdora,0000,0000,0000,,Just a few more...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:24.92,main,Mimosa,0000,0000,0000,,You're okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.01,0:13:28.72,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,One after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.71,0:13:33.64,main,Klaus,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.64,0:13:39.69,main,Hamon,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness, you saved me.\NI'll treat you to some gelato later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:44.11,main,Sol,0000,0000,0000,,Take that, and that, and that, and that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.65,0:13:49.41,main,Charlotte,0000,0000,0000,,Every rose has its thorns.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:51.79,main,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,Mist Spider's Threads.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:57.66,main,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,Water Creation Magic: Holy Water Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.55,0:14:08.51,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,That brat's your prey this time, Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.51,0:14:15.68,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You just keep bringing out these \Ncreepy things one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:17.39,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,No fair, you jerk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.15,0:14:21.19,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,My wound opened up even more?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.62,0:14:24.96,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Jimmy got you with one of his\Nspecially made curse shells.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:27.03,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,It's loaded with curse power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.44,0:14:30.43,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Even scratches won't stop bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.63,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be real careful if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:33.59,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:40.58,italics,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to swing \Nmy big sword fast enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:46.74,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You sure are a pain for a brat \Nthat doesn't have any magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.74,0:14:50.34,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,But Jimmy's still got \Nlots of curse power left.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.47,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but before we deal with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:03.40,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Jimmy, finish off that eyesore \Nof a brat back there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.99,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you aiming at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:19.04,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right. I guess you Magic Knights\Nprotect the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.21,0:15:29.34,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Just abandon her already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:36.72,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. There's no point in getting hurt \Njust to protect others, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.72,0:15:38.18,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mister...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:43.89,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,What do you gain from protecting a little \Nbrat like that, you hypocritical loser?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.05,0:15:48.52,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect her, even if I \Ndon't gain anything from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.11,0:15:53.31,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Will you? I see. Then stay right there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.31,0:15:57.83,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,and swing your sword around until \Nyou bleed to death, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.08,0:16:05.96,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Asta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.56,0:16:09.34,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I have to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.34,0:16:18.80,flashback,Solid,0000,0000,0000,,You can't even control your magic. \NYou're such an embarrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:22.95,flashback,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,You've basically been exiled \Nfrom the Silva family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.95,0:16:26.40,flashback,Nebra,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you had the nerve \Nto return to the Noble Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.18,0:16:29.90,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,You do not belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:31.28,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,Begone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.41,0:16:34.87,flashback,Nozel,0000,0000,0000,,failure that killed our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.75,0:16:38.25,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't... Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:41.83,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Someone... Please, someone help Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:55.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Thank y—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:58.97,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:02.97,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.88,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Black Bulls girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.61,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,you're not letting what your \Nsiblings said get to you, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:14.40,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time for that on the battlefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.63,0:17:18.69,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,One wrong decision and a life could be lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.99,0:17:24.87,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,You're standing here right now \Nas a member of the Magic Knights!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.23,0:17:29.07,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,If you joined the Magic Knights \Nof your own free will,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.51,0:17:31.81,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,then steel yourself and get stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:33.34,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Steel myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.87,0:17:36.01,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,Being weak is nothing to be ashamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:40.01,main,Fuegoleon,0000,0000,0000,,However, staying weak is!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:44.19,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.29,0:17:48.24,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who proved that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.48,0:17:53.45,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,If he can do it, I can also...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.73,0:17:59.24,italics,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.92,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:13.33,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,The weak will always die weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.80,0:18:21.64,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.44,0:18:23.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.85,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.85,0:18:36.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Noelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:39.24,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Stupidsta?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.60,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I can't bear to just sit and watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.60,0:18:44.58,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you, so you'd better be grateful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:45.41,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.78,0:18:48.61,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he can stop \Nyou if you can move freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:49.72,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.58,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:55.00,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,I was never feeling down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.05,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.01,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so full of yourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:10.80,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,I shall assist you, my rival!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.80,0:19:16.36,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,Get that bastard good! \NShow me your true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:20.28,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:21.99,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.99,0:19:26.69,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,And I was going to do that anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet! I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:49.26,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Whoops...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.27,0:19:53.48,main,Noelle,0000,0000,0000,,You did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:55.10,main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Mister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.10,0:20:00.56,main,Leopold,0000,0000,0000,,You don't fight like any other mage!\NYou're just too interesting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:08.76,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:13.83,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let that ridiculous \Nattack get to you, Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.80,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Jimmy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:17.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Stop blabbering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.75,0:20:20.38,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.38,0:20:26.08,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Wha? Don't get cocky, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.21,0:20:29.24,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.79,0:20:39.90,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Number Two, Alfred.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.40,0:20:44.85,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Alfred!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.72,0:21:07.72,main,Yuno,0000,0000,0000,,Asta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:33.74,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,My dry emotions gaze at the me from that day
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.74,0:21:36.71,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And push me forward
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:38.75,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I can't find a place to go)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.75,0:21:44.03,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the faintest light can \Nstill break through the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.03,0:21:49.53,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And change the flow of time
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.26,0:21:51.95,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(I will keep believing in you)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:54.83,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In this ever-vivid place
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.83,0:21:57.77,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Break free yourself)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.67,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to grasp my endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.67,0:22:03.33,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is a path that I should choose
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.33,0:22:05.39,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(Do you wanna try? Do you wanna try?)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:08.30,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wherever it may lead us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.30,0:22:10.79,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Until my life comes to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:13.47,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will accept any pain that comes my way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.49,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,(We can try again, we can try again)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.49,0:22:19.85,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we can't see tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.85,0:22:25.40,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding onto feelings too intense to voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:29.13,italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep screaming them in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:44.48,sign_33083_276_Petit_Clover_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,520)}Pe{\c&H3BC020&}t{\c&HE2AF0F&}i{\c&H3BC020&}t C{\c&HE2AF0F&}l{\c&H3BC020&}o{\c&H0E42D4&}ve{\c&H3BC020&}r
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.92,0:22:43.48,main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Petit Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.25,0:22:47.98,sign_33188_278_The_Mystery_of_t,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(520,1)}Ra
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:45.64,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:49.31,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:50.55,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.55,0:22:52.32,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Asta. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.74,0:22:56.25,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So, you haven't actually said \Nyour name in the show yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.25,0:22:58.33,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Could you tell us what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:01.08,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my name is Rades.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.33,0:23:01.08,italicstop,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,(Hai, ore no namae wa Radesu desu.)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:03.59,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Radesdes? I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.59,0:23:05.84,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So where did you come from, Radesdes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:09.08,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not Radesdes. \NYou don't need the "des."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.08,0:23:11.98,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need the des? \NSo your name is just Ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.11,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you calling Ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.11,0:23:14.66,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you said there was no "des."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.66,0:23:17.64,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rades! I just mean \Nyou don't need the "des."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.64,0:23:19.60,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's Radesdes, but you don't need the "des"...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.60,0:23:22.29,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,So if you take out all the "des,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.29,0:23:23.24,main,Asta,0000,0000,0000,,It's just Ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:28.65,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you that's not right!\NI'm Rades! Rades!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.65,0:23:34.13,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,You better remember that, you useless brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.67,0:23:39.16,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,The Magic Knights are no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:41.91,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,I, Rades, am the strongest of them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.33,0:23:47.00,main,rades,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Black Clover{\i0}, Page 23:\N"The Crimson Lion King."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.58,0:23:51.14,sign_34238_338_Page_2_The_Boys_,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(234,1)}Page 23\N\N{\fs18} The Crimson Lion King
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:49.88,main,Rades,0000,0000,0000,,Controlling corpses is my magic!
